    "In this paper, α defaults to 0.5.",
    "(f) Objective metrics: Because of the non-equilibrium nature of the positive and negative sample sizes for the keyframe screening task, we use only the F1 score to objectively assess the quality of the keyframe recommendations, for which we need to calculate the precision P and the recall R first.",
    "P N um mk N um rk,where the overall keyframe-recommendation precision P is the ratio of the number of matches between the recommended keyframes and ground-truth construction (N um mk) to the number of all recommended keyframes (N um rk).",
    "R N um mk N um gtk,where the recall rate R is the ratio of N um mk to the number of keyframes in ground-truth construction (N um gtk).F 2 * P * R P + R,where F score take into account the results of the model's accuracy and completeness calculations, favoring the indicator with the smaller value.",
    "In this paper, we calculate the average of all the labeler's F score and the best one among them separately."
